{"type":"text","timestamp":1777749909184,"sessionID":"ses_215dc43d0ffeTSFoJdpYte7q4z","part":{"id":"prt_dea26cb1a001YRAUprOzPTZy2k","messageID":"msg_dea268fd5001jnv42lPFFJT0gz","sessionID":"ses_215dc43d0ffeTSFoJdpYte7q4z","type":"text","text":"Now I have full context. Let me write the hypothesis file. All prior attempts were branch-prediction related; the structural category has only had one attempt (moving branch resolution). Dual-issue is the natural next structural step, and the NRET=2 contract already supports it.","time":{"start":1777749904154,"end":1777749909180}}}
