{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777747139025,"sessionID":"ses_2160609d6ffeKHNoQWjRqR0FjP","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_00_y3YOTNDafTH0edr3MTM76924","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore prior experiments","prompt":"Search the codebase for any prior experiments related to branch prediction or the \"predictor\" category. Specifically:\n1. Read cores/bench/LESSONS.md if it exists\n2. Read cores/bench/experiments/log.jsonl if it exists, searching for \"predictor\" or \"branch\" or \"BTB\" or \"BHT\" or \"gshare\"\n3. List files in cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/ if it exists\n4. Check if there's a schemas/hypothesis.schema.json file for the exact schema requirements\n\nReturn ALL findings - full content of LESSONS.md, all relevant log lines, and the hypothesis schema.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_216053102ffeQtUuZiGA5bfsg9 (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere are my complete findings across all four items:\n\n---\n\n## 1. `cores/bench/LESSONS.md`\n\n**Does not exist.** No lessons file has been created for this core.\n\n---\n\n## 2. `cores/bench/experiments/log.jsonl` — branch prediction entries\n\n**No branch prediction experiments exist in the log.** The log contains exactly 1 entry — the baseline retest:\n\n```json\n{\"id\": \"baseline-bench-a3930e2\", \"title\": \"Baseline retest for cores/bench\", \"category\": \"micro_opt\", \"outcome\": \"improvement\", \"fitness\": 301.04, \"delta_pct\": 0.0, \"vs_baseline\": 0.0, \"fmax_mhz\": 135.21, \"ipc_coremark\": 2e-06, \"cycles\": 4491485, \"iterations\": 10, \"lut4\": 9880, \"ff\": 1858, \"seeds\": [121.29, 135.21, 136.07], \"formal_passed\": true, \"cosim_passed\": true, \"error\": null, \"implementation_notes\": \"\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-02T18:35:51.802352Z\", \"round_id\": 0, \"slot\": 0}\n```\n\nNo matches were found anywhere in the workspace for the strings `\"predictor\"` in any JSON log or hypothesis file, nor for `BTB`, `BHT`, or `gshare`.\n\n---\n\n## 3. `cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/` — file listing\n\nThe directory exists but contains **no hypothesis JSON files**. It has only three hidden agent session logs (from the first round's three slots: micro_opt, structural, predictor) and a `.gitkeep`:\n\n| File | Content |\n|------|---------|\n| `cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/.agent.hyp-20260502-001-r1s0.log` | Agent session log for slot 0 (micro_opt) — started reading log.jsonl and searching for LESSONS.md/hypotheses, then stopped after 1 step. |\n| `cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/.agent.hyp-20260502-002-r1s1.log` | Agent session log for slot 1 (structural) — only a `step_start` event, no tool calls. |\n| `cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/.agent.hyp-20260502-003-r1s2.log` | Agent session log for slot 2 (**predictor**) — only a `step_start` event, no tool calls. The session appears to have aborted before any hypothesis was written. |\n\nThe agent logs show that round 1 had a `predictor` slot (slot 2), but the agent session died at `step_start` with zero tool calls — meaning **no predictor hypothesis was ever generated or evaluated**.\n\nOther files in the experiments directory:\n- `cores/bench/experiments/progress.png` — a plot of fitness progress\n- `cores/bench/experiments/.gitkeep`\n\n---\n\n## 4. `schemas/hypothesis.schema.json` — full schema\n\nFull path: `/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs-pilot/deepseek-v4-pro-rep1/schemas/hypothesis.schema.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\",\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"required\": [\"id\",\"title\",\"category\",\"motivation\",\"hypothesis\",\"expected_impact\",\"changes\"],\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"id\":       {\"type\": \"string\", \"pattern\": \"^hyp-[0-9]{8}-[0-9]{3}(-r[0-9]+s[0-9]+)?$\"},\n    \"title\":    {\"type\": \"string\", \"minLength\": 5},\n    \"category\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"micro_opt\",\"structural\",\"extension\",\"predictor\",\"memory\"]},\n    \"motivation\":  {\"type\": \"string\", \"minLength\": 20},\n    \"hypothesis\":  {\"type\": \"string\", \"minLength\": 20},\n    \"expected_impact\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"required\": [\"fitness_delta_pct\",\"confidence\"],\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"fitness_delta_pct\": {\"type\": \"integer\"},\n        \"confidence\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"low\",\"medium\",\"high\"]}\n      }\n    },\n    \"changes\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\", \"minItems\": 1,\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"file\",\"description\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"file\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"Must be under rtl/ (any extension) or be a test/test_*.py cocotb suite. Anything else is rejected by the runtime sandbox check.\",\n            \"pattern\": \"^(rtl/[^.].*|test/test_[^/]+\\\\.py)$\"\n          },\n          \"description\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Additional context: current branch-related RTL\n\nThe `cores/bench/rtl/` directory has **no branch prediction module** (no BTB, BHT, gshare, etc.). The core is a pure 5-stage in-order pipeline. Branch handling exists only in:\n\n- **`decoder.sv`** — classifies instructions via `branch_op` (3-bit funct3) and `is_branch` flag\n- **`ex_stage.sv`** — resolves all branches in the EX stage (combinational evaluation of BEQ/BNE/BLT/BGE/BLTU/BGEU), computes `redirect`/`redirect_target`, flushes IF/ID on taken branches\n- **`hazard_unit.sv`** — receives `redirect` to trigger pipeline flush\n- **`if_stage.sv`** — receives `redirect` to update PC\n- **`core_pkg.sv`** — defines `branch_taken` and `branch_target` in the EX/MEM pipeline register struct\n\nThe tournament system's diversity rotation maps slot 2 to the `\"predictor\"` category (see `tools/tournament.py` line 61, test assertion `tools/test_tournament.py` line 28), confirming branch prediction is a designated experiment category — it just has never been attempted yet in this core's history.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_216053102ffeQtUuZiGA5bfsg9","model":{"modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro","providerID":"opencode-go"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore prior experiments","time":{"start":1777747021573,"end":1777747139024}},"id":"prt_de9fab84c0019WFdlVJjXn1osz","sessionID":"ses_2160609d6ffeKHNoQWjRqR0FjP","messageID":"msg_de9f9f677001Q59P9v89x9W6u7"}}
